QuestData.Title: Strange Tools
QuestData.Description: We are well on our way to building our first ship, but unfortunately, I am not the orc for the job. I have no idea how to work with these human tools. Your shipwright, Yanas Seastrike, is going to take over from here on out.$b$bI will be here at the dry docks if you need anything from me.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Speak with Yanas Seastrike at the dry docks. His shipbuilding work is renowned.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Yanas Seastrike at the dry docks.
QuestData.RewardText: Interested in shipbuilding, I see? I will do everything I can to help out, commander.
